      "timestamp": "2025-11-29T07:38:36.878+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "These rules are documented here:\n- https://gf180mcu-pdk.readthedocs.io/en/latest/physical_verification/design_manual/drm_11_1.html\n- https://gf180mcu-pdk.readthedocs.io/en/latest/physical_verification/design_manual/drm_11_2.html\n\nSo it should be possible to submit your own custom cells based on these rules, but there is no guarantee that they will work as expected.",
      "author": {
